beer.beer_description:
A premium light beer manufactured according to a traditional German recipe, having a unique color of ripe wheat and lush and firm beer head.

In its composition, Starogradsko contains exclusively barley malt and hops, no other cereals, which is another proof of the premium quality of the beer, along with the use of pure spring Gorska water, as one of the main ingredients. Starogradsko is manufactured with modern microbiological membrane filtration, by means of which the beer retains its original flavor and freshness and is still unpasteurized. Starogradsko light contains 4.5% alcohol and can be found in glass packaging of 0.33 l disposable packaging.

Light for drinking, tasty and premium, Starogradsko is meant for real beer enthusiasts.
